{"tid":2277012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 買netflix account中伏","createTime":"2020-11-08T07:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T08:05:20.000Z","uid":368273,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"da5912b68713eb66471d579b32da1bb5a60a541b","tid":2277012,"uid":368273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"代友po<br />\n話說同幾個friend一齊夾買netflix account平D<br />\n咁係ig見到有個都幾多人follow嘅賣家<br />\n就買咗個一年嘅private account (每月需換新account登入)<br />\n點知未用夠1個月 仲差幾日 個account已經失效咗<br />\n不過見仲差幾日就到下個月 就諗住當日先問佢拎新一個月嘅account<br />\n點知一問 隔咗大半日見佢online咗好多次都無覆就再問<br />\n佢就話咩D account有問題 依加只能夠退款或者加錢買6個月嘅plan<br />\n退款話只能退$260 我就話我個plan係$300 應該係退$300*11/12=$275<br />\n佢就隔咗2日完全冇覆過<br />\n到我2日後再問 佢就話sent 我一睇 佢退咗$300-$93=$207 仲寫住話 $93係original price<br />\n然後仲block埋whatsapp<br />\n只能哭喪同埋警戒各位唔好中佢伏 (sorry for using 支那寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n佢ig/carousell account: lucky_shop_hk_2020/luckyshop-hk<br />\n電話: 9563 8676/9258 5164<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSWmp8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSWmp8R.jpg&h=99371419&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j0hpnVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0hpnVz.jpg&h=2fa7c527&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJEfuAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJEfuAB.jpg&h=079c11f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ0RNnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ0RNnh.jpg&h=32ae735b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb13643cbcc67d42fc086e92d215e836d2454627","tid":2277012,"uid":163380,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"屌，用支那寶仲要成個乞衣咁幾十蚊都慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c503909465e8b34b19bbb8c06ae9c233d98b5b7","tid":2277012,"uid":88510,"like":4,"d